Zari Hassan has gifted herself a brand new G-Wagon. The car is an addition to her car collection, whose number plates are customised. "I like the way he roar. Damn @yas_performance thanks for coming through with the customized badges, the mags and extras," she posted online. The current price for a G Wagon in Kenya is Sh15 million. In 2020, her baby daddy Diamond spent millions and bought her a brand new Bentley. Zari quickly thank him for the gift on Instagram. “Asante Baba Tee for the Top Up,” she captioned the video. In 2021, Zari took to social media to call out a fan who castigated her for living a flashy lifestyle. Zari Hassan told the fan he was speaking like the poor do.